description:
The book of Daniel told Gods people ahead of time what was to come. But it is also for Gods people today, telling us what is still to come. The book of Daniel affirms the validity of the Bible and confirms that all throughout history God has been in control. Many of the prophecies have to do with the rise and fall of kingdoms, telling us how they would rise to power, how they would be conquered, and who would come after them. Because its amazing prophetic insights have been so accurate, some have claimed that the book of Daniel was written long after the events it predicted. But this argument has been refuted by archeological findings, proving once again that the Bible is a trustworthy source of information.

Watch full lecture here: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xPQjYqk_mI8&t=11s
